lead_paragraph: As former secretary of state Hillary Clinton weighs a run for president in 2016, at least a dozen independent groups, from the serious to the mysterious, have sprung up to raise money in her name.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Not Running (Yet), but Groups Use Her Name to Raise Money
